Ion iriac and Guillermo Vilas were the defending champions but did not compete that year. Jimmy Connors and Brian Gottfried won in the final 76, 62 against Kevin Curren and Steve Denton. Champion seeds are indicated in bold text while text in italics indicates the round in which those seeds were eliminated. 
